Glad to revisit this beautiful music once again.

snippet.textDisplay:
Understanding what fusion is and how it can embellish music is the work of learned musicians. India is full of learned musicians. Mix of levels of different instruments and sounds requires very good understanding of its final effect. Arrangers are not only great musicians but they know how to control the sounds and effects of an orchestra.
But the trend in India is to make mockery out of music and that is in very poor taste. Of course I don’t have to listen to rubbish but cannot pardon buffoons for ruining the tastes of youngsters. If you can’t better something don’t at least ruin it. Even Coke is a formula by which Coke has become a mega business.

snippet.textDisplay:
Vanisha, I knew it would fly over your head. No I don’t hate anyone or anything. Art is a very constructed effort. Art is not any rubbish. The various genres in music all have a typical aspect and then within it there is freedom to create multitudes of new variations. But these are all concerted and methodical efforts. Law of nature has naturally designed the human mind to appreciate perfection but this mechanic can be perverted by continuously feeding the mind with the wrong message
Next time take it a step further, get instrumentalists to play who can’t play at all and see if it washes with the least educated.
